## s1: deny everything, then re-allow all (except a few) directories for Git to descend into
*
!**/

## s2: then re-allow wanted files at any depth
!.gitignore
!.clauderc
!*.md
!*.base
!*.txt
!*.json
!*.sh
!*.plist
!*.js
!*.ts

## s3. then re-deny unwanted files that were allowed too loosely in s2

# repo-skeleton local private workspace; keep untracked even when it is a symlink
repo-skeleton/private
repo-skeleton/private/**
